Rating: 3
At first, I was a bit apprehensive about this dish. I first prepared the dressing and I tasted it as I always do and found it too salty. But, when mixed with the apples & potatoes it worked like magic. My only problem with the dish is that my dressing was a bit "runny". I will try again next time with a small dab of flour to thicken the dressing.